    {
        "url": "/quotes/hans_urs_von_balthasar_358415",
        "quote": "The Christian response is contained in these two fundamental dogmas: that of the Trinity and that of the Incarnation. In the trinitarian dogma God is one, good, true, and beautiful because he is essentially Love, and Love supposes the one, the other, and their unity.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Hans Urs von Balthasar",
            "url": "/quotes/hans_urs_von_balthasar_358415"
